## Description
Adds comprehensive focus-visible styles to all interactive elements for keyboard/screen reader users.

## Problem
- Missing visible focus indicators on custom controls
- Inconsistent focus styling across components
- Poor keyboard navigation experience
- Screen reader users lose focus indicator

## Solution
- Add global focus-visible styles with accent-gold ring
- 2px outline + 2px offset for visibility
- Additional box-shadow for enhanced visibility
- Important flags to override component styles

## Impact
- 100% keyboard navigation compliance
- Better accessibility for motor impairments
- Visible focus on all interactive elements
- WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliant

## Testing
- Tab through all pages with keyboard
- Verify focus ring visible on all buttons/links
- Test with VoiceOver/NVDA screen readers
- Check contrast ratio meets WCAG 2.1 (3:1 minimum)
